---
import Tip from "../../components/Tip.astro";
import DlcLayout from "../../layouts/DlcLayout.astro";
const baseUrl = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<DlcLayout title="Ashes of Elrant Introduction">
  <div class="hero">
    <img
      src={`${baseUrl}logo-dlc.png`}
      alt="Ashes of Elrant DLC"
      class="hero-logo"
    />
    <p class="subtitle">An Interactive Walkthrough</p>
  </div>

  <section class="content-section" id="intro">
    <h2>Introduction</h2>

    <div class="handwritten">
      <p>
        Welcome to our Chained Echoes: Ashes of Elrant DLC (2025) walkthrough
        and guide! With this guide you can expect a full walkthrough from
        beginning to end with strategies for every dungeon, every quest, every
        sidequest, strategies for every boss fight, and much more!
      </p>

      <p>
        Man does it feel good to be back! This game was one of my favorite back
        in 2022 and I even had no idea there was DLC coming out, but once I was
        notified, of course I was going to hop onboard and write a guide for it!
      </p>

      <p>
        This DLC is also quite crazy in terms of size. The story behind it is,
        at least so far where I am personally in the story, quite good. They've
        included a fishing minigame, a digging minigame (I hate this one haha)
        and many more things that make it a much more enjoyable experience.
      </p>

      <p>
        So follow me, as we venture into the world of Chained Echoes once more!
      </p>

      <p>
        <a
          href="https://www.neoseeker.com/chained-echoes/File:Vinheim_cursive.png"
        >
          <img
            src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/f/ff/Vinheim_cursive.png/80px-Vinheim_cursive.png"
            alt="Vinheim cursive.png"
          />
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="offer">
      <h3>What this guide will offer:</h3>

      <ul>
        <li>Complete walkthrough for the game from start to finish</li>
        <li>All Boss Strategies</li>
        <li>All Side Quests</li>
        <li>Important Collectables</li>
        <li>Much, much more!</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="controls">
      <h2>Controls</h2>

      <table class="controls-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>XBOX</th>
            <th>FUNCTION</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <img
                src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/8/80/VinXBA.png/23px-VinXBA.png"
                alt="XBOX A"
              />
            </td>
            <td>Use / Talk / Confirm</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <img
                src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/e/ee/VinXB.png/23px-VinXB.png"
                alt="XBOX B"
              />
            </td>
            <td>Cancel</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <img
                src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/6/65/VinXY.png/23px-VinXY.png"
                alt="XBOX Y"
              />
            </td>
            <td>Menu</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <img
                src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/d/d4/VinXX.png/23px-VinXX.png"
                alt="XBOX X"
              />
            </td>
            <td>Map</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <img
                src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/4/42/VinXRB.png/23px-VinXRB.png"
                alt="XBOX RB"
              />
            </td>
            <td>Switch Character (Battle), Call / Raise Sky Armor</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <img
                src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/9/94/VinXLB.png/23px-VinXLB.png"
                alt="XBOX LB"
              />
            </td>
            <td>Flee (Battle), Exit / Lower Sky Armor</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <img
                src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/1/19/VinXRT.png/23px-VinXRT.png"
                alt="XBOX RT"
              />
            </td>
            <td>Quest Log</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <img
                src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/6/62/VinXLT.png/23px-VinXLT.png"
                alt="XBOX LT"
              />
            </td>
            <td>Reward Board</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <img
                src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/d/d6/VinXMenu.png/23px-VinXMenu.png"
                alt="XBOX Menu"
              />
            </td>
            <td>Main Menu</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>
</DlcLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-logo {
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    max-height: 15rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .offer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .content-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .content-section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .handwritten {
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .handwritten p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .handwritten img {
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  .offer h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .offer ul {
    padding: 0;
    list-style-type: disc;
    margin-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .offer ul li {
    padding: 0.25rem 0;
  }

  .controls {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .controls-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    background-color: var(--card-bg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2));
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .controls-table th,
  .controls-table td {
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color, #444);
    padding: 0.75rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .controls-table th {
    background-color: var(--secondary-bg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4));
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    color: var(--primary-color, #f0c05a);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .controls-table td img {
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      padding: 2rem 0;
    }
    .hero-logo {
      max-height: 6rem;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
